    <item>
      <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 22:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>1.1.0 — bundle renamed</h2>
        <p>The app bundle is now <code>DXF Viewer.app</code> (with a space). The Dock, menu bar, About dialog, and Finder already showed "DXF Viewer"; this brings the on-disk filename and the Activity Monitor process name into line. <strong>If you pinned the app to the Dock, you'll need to re-pin it after this update.</strong></p>
        <p>Also relicensed from MIT to GPL-3.0.</p>
      ]]></description>
